Eugene Melnyk Reaches Settlement With OSC in Probe of Biovail Drugmaker

-- B y   G a r y   N o r r i s
-- 
2011-05-05T14:46:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/eugene-melnyk-reaches-settlement-with-osc-in-probe-of-biovail-drugmaker.html
Eugene Melnyk reached a settlement
with the Ontario Securities Commission in a probe of drugmaker
Biovail Corp. As part of the settlement presented to an OSC
panel in Toronto today, Melnyk agreed to pay C$565,000 in costs
and drop his appeal. Melnyk also faces a five-year ban as a
director or officer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Scanlan at 
 dscanlan@bloomberg.net  